The nascent ecosystem is expanding with the recent airdrop that has been received with mixed feelings from the community.
‚Äã
The following weeks and months will draw a clearer picture of the ecosystem and opportunities on the chain, which for the moment remains relatively traditional.
‚Äã
As highlighted in our previous post on Taiko, the chain puts a high emphasis on building advanced and highly complex technology at the cost of a developed and vibrant ecosystem.
‚Äã
https://t.co/P7VYFXElEA
‚Äã
Taiko currently has vague initiatives to develop the ecosystem, such as the grant program, but relatively little information on their future objectives and plans to become a leading scaling solution.
‚Äã
üß† Conclusion
‚Äã
In an ever-evolving blockchain industry where attention, liquidity, and efforts are continuously being fragmented, Taiko's solution to Ethereum scalability aims to provide new horizons.
‚Äã
Its sequencing approach aligns closely with Ethereum's values, although it (temporarily) has a higher operational cost compared to other scalability solutions that are out there.
‚Äã
The ecosystem development will play a crucial role in Taiko's growth over the following months, as user adoption and activity are key to a chain's success.
‚Äã
